    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "At Lat. 19°18' N. Long. 166°34' E.\n(Pacific\nOcean), where Wake Island is located, the tern\ndominates the bird life. Dark at wing-tip and\nPOST CARD\nwith body of such whiteness as to reflect in\nPLACE\nSTAMP\nHERE\nflight the brilliant coloring of the lagoon waters,\nADDRESS\nthe tern is found by the thousands at this unique\nstopping place on Pan American Airways trans-\npacific airline.\nSee he mit nearestersting\nas the gorys at midua\nex, nur manu\n+ Prew.\ntell you falle\nFove 2 the a Fee"
